Pro Football Hall of Famers
The Pro Football Hall of Fame has inducted eleven players who made their primary contribution to professional football while with the Raiders, in addition to owner Al Davis and head coach John Madden. The Raiders' total of thirteen Hall of Famers is tied for seventh-highest with the St. Louis Rams.96
