Retired numbers
The Raider organization does not retire the jersey numbers of former players. The number 00, worn by Jim Otto for his entire career, is no longer allowed by the NFL.97 It was originally permitted for him only by the AFL as a marketing gimmick since his jersey number 00 is a homonym pun of his name (aught-O).
